A \subset \mathbb{R}^2
D_1(0,0)
\mathbf{x}_0 = (1,0)
f: A \to \mathbb{R}, \, \mathbf{x} \mapsto f(\mathbf{x})
f(\mathbf{x})=1
 \lim_{\mathbf{x}\to\mathbf{x}_0} f(\mathbf{x})=1
A
\{x_n\}\subset A
\lim_n f(x_n) = 1
f\equiv 1
